Cannot display equator and tropics as an option ? No display of latitude and longitude even at the level of 10 degrees on a world over-view ? replyContent: Thanks for sharing your experience with the app. You will find decimal lat/lon & DMS val. by searching via the main search box on the app start page. You can also search by lat/lon either in map or main search. Equator is shown in world position map. Dateline and tropics display is in the dev. pipeline and will be added. Kind regards MxGeo Support

replyContent:
